{"tid":896333,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"心靈雞湯","createTime":"2018-11-10T02:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T03:21:36.000Z","uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a1ea4213b2fa8b90f449fad14042a373bc4ceb91","tid":896333,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T02:40:08.000Z","msg":"不要害怕一段關係結束，因為以你的條件，結束是必然的事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508614ae9faaa4c4903d78d0d920d789426ea020","tid":896333,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T02:42:38.000Z","msg":"與其暗戀，不如強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69150843ea36d7a0d5a457dafa0b874395f2748","tid":896333,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T02:43:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/10/104338_42433aa98b0b462d57990d8d46cf3466.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F10%2F104338_42433aa98b0b462d57990d8d46cf3466.gif&h=cf34ef4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7898c7444b2f9841cdceb04a981f297731bb29fc","tid":896333,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T02:45:14.000Z","msg":"幸福是站在父母的肩膊上，可惜你父母很矮，肩膊也很斜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d5991d82dc345cea0b1e3793009dc0ab3e4dbd","tid":896333,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T02:49:15.000Z","msg":"單戀就如你高孖展在 460 元的時候購入了很多手騰訊，當它給外資洗倉，反映了真實的價值，你可以在 IFC 天台跳下去了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8349befa1b70db9b7548f7ac89bfe99e6ad15b","tid":896333,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T02:51:18.000Z","msg":"香港人只有兩種，一種就是李澤楷，其餘的都是幫李澤楷打工的畜生<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49600c0a1b1cf6cffb3b694b2662c17ee99c9168","tid":896333,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T02:58:45.000Z","msg":"你為甚麼找不到女友？<br />\n<br />\n因為當李澤楷一星期付出了七天的時間找女友，你就付出了五天的時間替他工作，只有在剩餘兩天找女友。<br />\n<br />\n他比你們努力得多呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c1977dc846171308cb665bcf360a2f1f22fe8d","tid":896333,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T03:01:15.000Z","msg":"有錢人中出即飛，再掉進窮人的回收箱裡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d0b724c77c8f52b598aaeb1b80b76386e6b03b","tid":896333,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T03:02:48.000Z","msg":"你的撚多硬，不如我財力有多厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee49219ca5e79ce80cf034ab4303f3fb5475b52","tid":896333,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T03:03:05.000Z","msg":"冷靜啲"},{"pid":"e8271c0ec4401ed4dbaee321486539722e49a8e7","tid":896333,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eee49219ca5e79ce80cf034ab4303f3fb5475b52","tid":896333,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T03:03:05.000Z","msg":"冷靜啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T03:04:09.000Z","msg":"冷靜一點，認清楚你就是一件廢物<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63cdf094499e9fc135a5c3f363398200cd2923c6","tid":896333,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T03:06:31.000Z","msg":"不想給戴帽，先用青洲英泥塗滿另一半的私處<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59e43786ed645aed6be2cb7e0d91ed94a039210","tid":896333,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T03:08:48.000Z","msg":"當你懂得製作屎坑雞的時候，你已經覺悟了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334bf0d408f030b8c4ea644e6611859ed307292f","tid":896333,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T03:11:17.000Z","msg":"錢買不到